ew scientific evidence suggests a possible miscarriage of justice.\n\nFrom [00:01:54] to [00:01:59], a close-up of the \"60 MINUTES\" clock is shown, along with additional material credits for \"The Mules of Instagram: Around the World with 30 Kilos\" by Urbania Media.",
